Jill Esmond https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jill_Esmond 0 Jill Esmond (born Jill Esmond Moore, 26 January 1908 – 28 July 1990) was an English stage and screen actress. She was the first wife of Laurence Olivier. Jill_Esmond ( born Jill_Esmond_Moore , 26_January_1908 – 28_July_1990 ) was an_English_stage_and_screen_actress .
